06/04/2010
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Hollywood star couple Angelina Jolie and Brad Pitt arrived unexpectedly to BiH on Monday (April 5th). They visited a refugee camp near the town of Gorazde and met families in the camp. According to local media reports, the visit aimed to highlight problems of refugees and displaced people in BiH. Jolie is the UNHCR Goodwill Ambassador. After the visit, the couple headed for Montenegro. (Dnevni Avaz, Onsa, Fena, RTRS - 05/04/10)
